00:01:33,932 --> 00:01:36,688
=The Sun in the Dark=

26
00:01:36,776 --> 00:01:39,008
=Episode 23=

27
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:42,579
My loyalty lies with the Night Deity.

28
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,219
Whoever holds

29
00:01:44,859 --> 00:01:45,980
that title gains my loyalty.

30
00:01:47,299 --> 00:01:48,780
Now that the mantle has shifted,

31
00:01:49,260 --> 00:01:50,299
my service naturally

32
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:52,819
transfers accordingly.

33
00:01:53,459 --> 00:01:55,299
Wisdom favors the adaptable.

34
00:01:55,859 --> 00:01:58,620
I appreciate clever people like him.

35
00:01:59,299 --> 00:02:00,180
Bai Xiaoying,

36
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,299
your vital essence is depleted,

37
00:02:02,459 --> 00:02:03,780
and you're dying.

38
00:02:04,099 --> 00:02:05,780
Let me hasten your journey.

39
00:02:06,219 --> 00:02:07,219
Die!

40
00:02:08,659 --> 00:02:09,379
Go!

41
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:11,979
Master.

42
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:12,979
Go now!

43
00:02:19,699 --> 00:02:20,580
Father, stop!

44
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,740
Please don't harm Yunya.

45
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:25,419
He released our enemy,

46
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:27,699
and you're pleading for him?

47
00:02:27,979 --> 00:02:28,780
Step back now!

48
00:02:28,979 --> 00:02:29,699
Father,

49
00:02:30,539 --> 00:02:32,460
why did you become the Night Deity?

50
00:02:32,979 --> 00:02:34,780
Tell me this isn't true.

51
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:35,740
Father,

52
00:02:36,259 --> 00:02:37,500
return with me.

53
00:02:38,259 --> 00:02:39,819
As my daughter,

54
00:02:40,099 --> 00:02:41,139
you cower like a mouse

55
00:02:41,659 --> 00:02:42,580
and whimper endlessly.

56
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:43,580
Get away!

57
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:44,860
Father,

58
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:47,460
as the Immortal Lord
of the Nine Heavens,

59
00:02:47,539 --> 00:02:49,259
you've always opposed the Night Deity.

60
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:51,379
How could you become what you hated?

61
00:02:51,699 --> 00:02:52,699
I don't believe it.

62
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:53,460
Father,

63
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:55,699
I beg you to stop this madness.

64
00:02:55,699 --> 00:02:56,300
Father,

65
00:02:56,699 --> 00:02:58,900
please stop doing this.

66
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,060
I have carefully schemed,

67
00:03:01,539 --> 00:03:02,659
using Ye Chenyuan

68
00:03:02,659 --> 00:03:05,099
to extract the Night Deity's power
from Bai Xiaoying.

69
00:03:05,979 --> 00:03:07,580
Why would I stop now?

70
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:09,900
I only regret not realizing sooner

71
00:03:10,259 --> 00:03:14,180
Night Deity's power could be converted
to serve my purpose over a millennium.

72
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:17,699
Now that I've achieved godhood,

73
00:03:18,259 --> 00:03:20,219
I'll no longer need

74
00:03:20,379 --> 00:03:21,539
the Night Deity's power

75
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:22,979
to balance Three Realms!

76
00:03:24,139 --> 00:03:26,979
Three Realms shall obey me now!

77
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:31,259
The universe
will be unified under my rule!

78
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:58,460
Good child,

79
00:03:59,219 --> 00:04:00,219
dry your tears.

80
00:04:02,259 --> 00:04:04,539
Though I'm now the Night Deity,

81
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:06,860
I remain your father.

82
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:10,099
You're still my beloved daughter.

83
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,340
Nothing changes that.

84
00:04:13,379 --> 00:04:16,100
I'm the ruler of the Three Realms,

85
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:19,259
and you'll be revered as my princess.

86
00:04:19,699 --> 00:04:20,699
Why weep?

87
00:04:21,139 --> 00:04:23,019
You should rejoice.

88
00:04:30,019 --> 00:04:32,100
You don't recognize your own father?

89
00:04:35,939 --> 00:04:38,139
Your public defiance today

90
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,980
will be forgiven

91
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,100
as first offense.

92
00:04:42,699 --> 00:04:50,779
But repeat this insolence, and you'll
cease to be my cherished daughter.

93
00:04:51,819 --> 00:04:53,060
Understood?

94
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:58,420
I

95
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,579
understood.

96
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:08,139
That's my good girl.

97
00:05:08,699 --> 00:05:10,939
Whether daughter of the Night Deity

98
00:05:10,939 --> 00:05:12,819
or daughter of the Immortal Lord,

99
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:15,500
obey me faithfully,

100
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,540
and my favor will never waver.

101
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:50,339
Yunya,

102
00:05:50,939 --> 00:05:53,139
you were my disciple before.

103
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:56,540
Releasing Bai Xiaoying was unforgivable,

104
00:05:57,620 --> 00:06:00,379
but leading the assault
against immortal sect

105
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,339
redeemed you.

106
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:03,660
From now on,

107
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:07,060
pledge loyalty to me alone.

108
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:11,459
Thank you for your mercy.

109
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,579
I freed Bai Xiaoying

110
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:15,620
to repay her favor.

111
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:19,860
Now that her heart
belongs to Ye Chenyuan,

112
00:06:20,779 --> 00:06:21,540
I'll show

113
00:06:22,139 --> 00:06:23,699
no mercy next time.

114
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:25,379
Good.

115
00:06:26,139 --> 00:06:27,220
In that case,

116
00:06:27,379 --> 00:06:30,620
I'll arrange a wedding.

117
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:33,500
Wanyan is of marriageable age.

118
00:06:33,779 --> 00:06:35,339
She admires you deeply.

119
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:37,939
You're my most trusted person.

120
00:06:38,579 --> 00:06:39,860
Having you marrying her

121
00:06:40,019 --> 00:06:41,819
brings me peace.

122
00:06:44,699 --> 00:06:46,300
Thank you, my lord.

123
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,100
Don't forget

124
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,620
I have raised you up.

125
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:12,240
and taught you martial arts.

126
00:07:13,139 --> 00:07:14,819
Every move and technique you know

127
00:07:15,139 --> 00:07:17,379
was personally taught by me.

128
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,579
Everything you possess

129
00:07:20,339 --> 00:07:22,379
is my bestowment upon you.

130
00:07:24,019 --> 00:07:25,819
Everything I have

131
00:07:26,579 --> 00:07:28,139
was earned through righteous means.

132
00:07:29,139 --> 00:07:30,920
But can you say the same?

133
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:35,459
Without my favor

134
00:07:35,459 --> 00:07:37,100
and efforts to elevate your status,

135
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,060
how could someone as young as you

136
00:07:39,259 --> 00:07:41,019
ascend to Upper Immortal?

137
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:45,060
I only chose you

138
00:07:45,939 --> 00:07:47,060
because you followed

139
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,980
every command of mine.

140
00:07:49,379 --> 00:07:52,019
That's why you were selected.

141
00:07:54,779 --> 00:07:56,860
If I'd known earlier,

142
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:59,500
I should have acted like this earlier.

143
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,980
You were always submissive.

144
00:08:02,939 --> 00:08:05,459
I didn't expect you'd betray me.

145
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:09,500
Do you know the best punishment

146
00:08:10,019 --> 00:08:11,939
for a traitor like you?

147
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:16,060
To turn you into a mindless puppet

148
00:08:16,699 --> 00:08:20,139
who serves me faithfully.

149
00:08:41,019 --> 00:08:41,820
Yunya.

150
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:45,659
Will you betray me again?

151
00:08:48,139 --> 00:08:51,019
I will never betray you, Master.

152
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,860
Good.

153
00:08:53,539 --> 00:08:57,500
You remain my favorite disciple.

154
00:09:39,179 --> 00:09:40,179
This place is secure.

155
00:09:42,139 --> 00:09:43,580
We'll rest here temporarily.

156
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,679
I made your favorite dishes.

157
00:10:19,059 --> 00:10:19,639
Try them.

158
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,360
It smells wonderful.

159
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:30,179
I'm craving some fruits.

160
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:31,740
How about

161
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:33,740
you go pick some?

162
00:10:34,019 --> 00:10:34,500
Alright.

163
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:13,539
(My body can't hold on)

164
00:11:14,299 --> 00:11:15,860
(much longer.)

165
00:11:23,179 --> 00:11:23,899
(Now,)

166
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:26,580
(my father has grown crazier,)

167
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,019
(but I remain powerless to stop him.)

168
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:34,139
(I don't know what he's done to Yunya.)

169
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,419
(What should I do?)

170
00:11:44,659 --> 00:11:46,279
Check out my daughter's dowry.

171
00:11:47,820 --> 00:11:49,860
Such magnificent bridal treasures.

172
00:11:50,299 --> 00:11:51,019
Well?

173
00:11:51,659 --> 00:11:52,460
Do you like them?

174
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,360
Wanyan.

175
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:57,899
Ask for anything else you desire.

176
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,120
I'll grant all your wishes.

177
00:12:01,899 --> 00:12:03,059
Everything you prepared

178
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:04,940
is to my liking.

179
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:07,899
That's my good daughter.

180
00:12:10,419 --> 00:12:12,100
I've always said

181
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:14,019
if you obey me faithfully,

182
00:12:14,139 --> 00:12:15,539
anything you want

183
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:17,179
shall be yours.

184
00:12:21,059 --> 00:12:22,279
I understand.

185
00:12:23,179 --> 00:12:24,220
Within this immortal sect,

186
00:12:24,899 --> 00:12:25,779
with you

187
00:12:26,179 --> 00:12:27,019
and Yunya by my side,

188
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:29,460
I am truly blessed.

189
00:12:33,179 --> 00:12:33,980
Father,

190
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:40,379
I want to personally select
items for our marital house.

191
00:12:41,220 --> 00:12:43,980
May I?

192
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:54,220
If you want to do it,

193
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:56,659
this shows your genuine happiness.

194
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:59,100
I shall grant this request.

195
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,879
But don't overexert yourself.

196
00:13:03,899 --> 00:13:04,539
So

197
00:13:05,059 --> 00:13:06,580
take Rong with you

198
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:08,100
when you go out.

199
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:11,539
She'll attend to your needs.

200
00:13:12,019 --> 00:13:13,419
This will ease my concerns.

201
00:13:19,139 --> 00:13:20,100
Thank you, Father.

202
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,059
Xiaoying.

203
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:55,139
What are you doing?

204
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,500
You misunderstood.

205
00:13:58,340 --> 00:13:59,539
I wasn't trying to die.

206
00:14:02,419 --> 00:14:03,299
Release me.

207
00:14:03,299 --> 00:14:03,740
No.

208
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:05,899
I'm afraid.

209
00:14:07,379 --> 00:14:08,539
Don't leave me.

210
00:14:15,379 --> 00:14:15,980
Don't worry.

211
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:17,860
I'll stay with you.

212
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:22,100
Don't worry.

213
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:23,700
I'm fine.

214
00:14:24,059 --> 00:14:24,539
Truly.

215
00:14:25,379 --> 00:14:25,899
Yeah.

216
00:14:32,259 --> 00:14:33,580
(Perhaps that thing)

217
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:36,100
(could help Xiaoying find peace.)

218
00:14:38,179 --> 00:14:39,740
(I should return to the immortal sect.)

219
00:14:50,899 --> 00:14:51,700
- Senior.
- Senior.

220
00:14:59,059 --> 00:14:59,980
It hurts!

221
00:15:00,059 --> 00:15:01,620
What's wrong?

222
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:03,700
I have sudden abdominal pain.

223
00:15:03,779 --> 00:15:05,100
Go fetch Immortal Xiyuan.

224
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:06,340
Maybe it's better

225
00:15:06,379 --> 00:15:08,220
if I help you go together.

226
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:09,139
I'll worry if you are

227
00:15:09,139 --> 00:15:10,059
left alone here.

228
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,100
Who's the master here?

229
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,379
I'm in such pain.

230
00:15:13,460 --> 00:15:14,419
I can barely move.

231
00:15:14,419 --> 00:15:15,019
Going with you

232
00:15:15,019 --> 00:15:16,259
might make me die on the way.

233
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,580
Besides,

234
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:18,860
we're in the sect.

235
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:20,220
I'm the lord's daughter.

236
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:21,419
No worries here.

237
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:22,299
Go now.

238
00:15:23,019 --> 00:15:23,940
I understand.

239
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:41,740
The Divine Sword fragments
are hard to find.

240
00:15:42,899 --> 00:15:44,860
It was clearly destroyed here that day.

241
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:02,399
Ye Chenyuan.

242
00:16:02,759 --> 00:16:03,440
It's you again?

243
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:06,080
It's me. Looking for what?

244
00:16:07,919 --> 00:16:08,519
Back off.

245
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:11,679
The Divine Sword
was used to kill your father.

246
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:13,559
Now, only fragments remain.

247
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,799
Why do you need them?

248
00:16:19,279 --> 00:16:20,740
I just want to find something

249
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:21,740
that can save my father.

250
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:25,559
My father isn't the Night Deity.

251
00:16:26,279 --> 00:16:28,100
He's just temporarily misguided.

252
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:29,919
I will save him.

253
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,919
Our suffering through lifetimes

254
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:38,159
now falls upon you.

255
00:16:41,279 --> 00:16:42,039
My father

256
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:44,440
has led the immortal sect
for over 1,500 years.

257
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,080
He once said,

258
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:47,440
"Killing the Night Deity"

259
00:16:47,759 --> 00:16:49,519
"is our duty."

260
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,960
As my father's daughter

261
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,440
and the Immortal Lord's heir,

262
00:16:53,759 --> 00:16:54,840
I swear I'll make it.

263
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:02,919
Yunya!

264
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:04,599
He seems off,

265
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:06,400
like being controlled.

266
00:17:11,559 --> 00:17:14,000
No wonder he didn't oppose our marriage.

267
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,640
I see.

268
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:18,279
Immortal sect fugitive.

269
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,759
I'll show no mercy.

270
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:27,960
Take the fragment and go!

271
00:17:28,759 --> 00:17:29,319
And you?

272
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:30,759
Don't worry.

273
00:17:31,799 --> 00:17:33,000
Yunya won't harm me.

274
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,200
Yunya!

275
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,400
I'm Wanyan.

276
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,079
Wake up, Yunya!

277
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,039
I'm Wanyan.

278
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,480
Yunya,

279
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:47,400
you were once the most uncompromising

280
00:17:47,799 --> 00:17:49,079
of the Nine Heavens.

281
00:17:50,039 --> 00:17:52,000
Do you realize what you've become?

282
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:54,079
Yunya, wake up now!

283
00:17:54,279 --> 00:17:56,039
Can you hear me, Yunya?

284
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:57,920
I'm Wanyan.

285
00:17:58,039 --> 00:17:59,880
Yunya, wake up!

286
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:03,960
Yunya.

287
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:05,799
Yunya.

288
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,980
I know you can hear me.

289
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:08,980
