294
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:16,359
but I'll stay here with you.

295
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,279
I won't leave.

296
00:18:17,519 --> 00:18:18,759
I'm not going anywhere, Yunya.

297
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:19,880
Wake up.

298
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,319
Wake up, Yunya.

299
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:22,759
Yunya.

300
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,359
