304
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:31,599
Yunya, you can do this.

305
00:18:31,599 --> 00:18:32,559
You won't lose.

306
00:18:47,519 --> 00:18:48,359
I never expected

307
00:18:49,559 --> 00:18:51,339
