310
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:01,440
Wanyan,

311
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,779
I don't know what happened.

312
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:08,119
Hold on.

313
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,900
You'll be fine.

314
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,200
This is the first time

315
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,559
I've seen you so panicked

316
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:20,220
for me.

317
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:21,759
Stop talking.

318
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,319
I'll take you to Immortal Xiyuan.

319
00:19:23,559 --> 00:19:24,559
She'll save you.

320
00:19:25,319 --> 00:19:26,119
Yunya,

321
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,559
you can't lose.

322
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:32,920
Don't let the Night Deity defeat you.

323
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:36,519
