326
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,000
But

327
00:19:46,519 --> 00:19:48,519
when I think about

328
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:51,140
our wedding ceremony in three days,

329
00:19:52,839 --> 00:19:54,119
I still feel somewhat

330
