334
00:20:08,779 --> 00:20:09,420
Wanyan.

335
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:11,619
Wanyan!

336
00:20:12,859 --> 00:20:13,539
Wanyan!

337
00:20:14,099 --> 00:20:15,779
Wanyan!

338
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,539
Wanyan!

339
00:20:48,059 --> 00:20:48,940
Why?

340
00:20:51,140 --> 00:20:52,140
Why?

341
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,259
Why

342
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:56,900
