364
00:22:36,339 --> 00:22:38,099
Surviving by chance like this

365
00:22:39,299 --> 00:22:40,539
and having these extra days

366
00:22:41,380 --> 00:22:42,579
are more than I could ask for.

367
00:22:45,299 --> 00:22:46,380
Don't worry about me.

368
00:22:46,859 --> 00:22:47,500
Promise me

369
00:22:48,059 --> 00:22:49,400
