370
00:22:50,099 --> 00:22:50,680
Okay?

371
00:23:02,859 --> 00:23:03,579
Yunya?

372
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:11,500
I'll kill you two.

373
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,819
This is revenge for Wanyan.

374
00:23:24,259 --> 00:23:25,460
This is inside Divine Sword.

375
00:23:27,019 --> 00:23:28,140
How can I still enter here?

376
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:33,500
Oh no! Ye Chenyuan is still outside.

377
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:48,359
You are

378
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:51,700
Divine Maiden Xi Wu?

379
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:53,460
Yes.

380
00:23:54,220 --> 00:23:54,740
But

381
00:23:55,099 --> 00:23:57,619
I perished 1,500 years ago.

382
00:23:58,299 --> 00:23:59,740
Only this wisp of my spirit remains

383
00:24:00,140 --> 00:24:01,500
within the Divine Sword.

384
00:24:02,259 --> 00:24:03,339
Now, I understand

385
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:05,779
it was to see you again.

386
00:24:06,339 --> 00:24:07,180
My daughter.

387
00:24:10,259 --> 00:24:11,099
Daughter...

388
00:24:13,420 --> 00:24:14,880
Such a distant word.

389
00:24:18,119 --> 00:24:20,559
I've long forgotten
what maternal love feels like.

390
00:24:22,460 --> 00:24:23,339
So

391
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,019
you're the one who made me

392
00:24:27,859 --> 00:24:28,960
the Night Deity's vessel?

393
00:24:30,339 --> 00:24:31,299
I'm sorry.

394
00:24:32,099 --> 00:24:33,420
If heaven had permitted,

395
00:24:33,619 --> 00:24:35,180
I would have watched you grow up.

396
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,980
Sealing the Night Deity within you

397
00:24:38,819 --> 00:24:41,500
was the only way to save humanity then.

398
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:43,480
It was only in that moment

399
00:24:44,259 --> 00:24:45,099
that I understood

400
00:24:45,779 --> 00:24:47,640
what fate demanded of me.

401
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:51,000
I had to harm my own child,

402
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:53,839
the person I loved most in this world.

403
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:55,859
You and Ye Chenyuan

404
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:58,420
have endured six lifetimes.

405
00:24:58,859 --> 00:24:59,740
In each lifetime,

406
00:25:00,259 --> 00:25:02,140
he was forced to kill you.

407
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:06,420
If you understand his pain,

408
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:07,740
then you know

409
00:25:08,220 --> 00:25:09,440
how I suffered.

410
00:25:11,220 --> 00:25:12,339
How deep could your pain be?

411
00:25:14,539 --> 00:25:15,920
You don't actually think

412
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,779
