413
00:25:20,019 --> 00:25:21,259
I'm filled with shame

414
00:25:22,099 --> 00:25:23,900
for making you bear such a fate

415
00:25:24,539 --> 00:25:27,180
and endless cycles of suffering.

416
00:25:27,900 --> 00:25:28,460
Ying,

417
00:25:29,299 --> 00:25:30,900
I don't seek your forgiveness.

418
00:25:31,539 --> 00:25:32,539
I just hope

419
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:35,839
you'll give me a chance to make amends.

420
00:25:41,579 --> 00:25:42,220
Now,

421
00:25:43,380 --> 00:25:45,019
the only thing I can give you

422
00:25:45,660 --> 00:25:47,619
is my final divine power

423
00:25:48,019 --> 00:25:50,420
sealed within the Divine Sword.

424
00:25:52,099 --> 00:25:54,339
I only wish for you
to protect yourself well

425
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:58,299
and live this life
in peace and happiness.

426
00:26:25,079 --> 00:26:26,099
What's happening to you?

427
00:26:27,099 --> 00:26:27,819
Ying,

428
00:26:29,019 --> 00:26:31,339
this is the last time I can see you.

429
00:26:32,259 --> 00:26:33,380
You must walk

430
00:26:34,099 --> 00:26:35,759
the road ahead alone.

431
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:38,119
If fate allows,

432
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:41,460
I hope you'll forgive
my willful decisions.

433
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:44,099
And I hope

434
00:26:45,180 --> 00:26:46,779
that you'll find peace within yourself.

435
00:26:50,099 --> 00:26:50,660
Mother!

436
00:26:55,220 --> 00:26:55,779
Mother!

437
00:27:09,839 --> 00:27:10,440
(This is)

438
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:12,359
(the Divine Sword.)

439
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,519
Immortal sect fugitive.

440
00:27:17,140 --> 00:27:18,579
I'll show no mercy.

441
00:27:24,619 --> 00:27:25,180
Leave now.

442
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,119
Go back and tell him

443
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:28,779
our lives

444
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:30,660
