454
00:28:26,019 --> 00:28:28,859
But I foolishly believed
Feng Changgeng's lies.

455
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:33,000
In the end,

456
00:28:34,180 --> 00:28:36,460
the devastation across the Three Realms

457
00:28:37,660 --> 00:28:39,299
is all my doing.

458
00:28:44,299 --> 00:28:46,019
Let's settle this
with him once and for all.

459
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:52,339
As long as I'm with you,

460
00:28:53,220 --> 00:28:54,440
